    {
      "id": "new-user-experience-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "New User Experience",
      "root": false,
      "position": {
        "x": -300,
        "y": -20
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 280,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# New User Experience\n\nThis mini-project models the first-run beta path as a small set of concrete graphs.\n\nWe are not assuming the right answer yet. The point is to make the onboarding arc visible, editable, and discussable in graph form.\n\nCurrent split:\n- first arrival\n- first successful interaction\n- save + return trust"
      }
    },
